body_html:
Hello @gerardocervantes8, I don't know about building with bazel for android but if you use the makefile building for android (tensorflow/contrib/makefile) you need to include the file tensorflow/core/kernels/data/iterator_ops.cc file in the tf_op_files.txt before compiling
Then the OpKernel for the 'Iterator' op should be included in the library
